      <title>圭亚那、苏里南选择中国公司建造价值2.36亿美元的桥梁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/guyana-suriname-pick-chinese-firm-to-build-236-million-bridge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圭亚那公共工程部长胡安·埃奇希尔周日表示，圭亚那和苏里南选定中国路桥公司来修建一座价值 2.36 亿美元的跨过科伦太因河连接这两个南美国家的大桥。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/guyana-suriname-pick-chinese-firm-to-build-236-million-bridge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 18:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，宏盟集团正就收购 Interpublic 进行深入谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/omnicom-is-in-advanced-talks-to-buy-interpublic-wsj-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华尔街日报》援引知情人士的话称，宏盟集团 (Omnicom Group Inc.) 正就收购埃培智集团 (Interpublic Group) 进行深入谈判，此次交易将打造出全球最大的广告公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/omnicom-is-in-advanced-talks-to-buy-interpublic-wsj-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 17:54:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚库尔德人庆祝阿萨德政权垮台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-08/syrian-kurds-celebrating-fall-of-assad-regime-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，数百名库尔德人在叙利亚东北部城市卡米什利庆祝巴沙尔·阿萨德政权的垮台。人们唱歌、向空中鸣枪，并高举被关押在土耳其的库尔德工人党 (PKK) 领导人阿卜杜拉·奥贾兰的海报来庆祝这一事件。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-08/syrian-kurds-celebrating-fall-of-assad-regime-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 14:35:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚人进入大马士革总统府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-08/syrians-enter-the-presidential-palace-in-damascus-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴沙尔·阿萨德政府垮台后，叙利亚人于周日进入大马士革总统府。阿萨德和其他高级官员失踪，下落不明。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-08/syrians-enter-the-presidential-palace-in-damascus-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 14:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人民币、欧元暴跌预示新兴市场货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/yuan-euro-rout-points-to-losses-for-emerging-market-currencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近几个月来，人民币和欧元的跌势进一步加剧，这导致亚洲和欧洲新兴市场货币的前景恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/yuan-euro-rout-points-to-losses-for-emerging-market-currencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
